title: Quantitative or Qualitative
text: We want to determine the type of calculator you use. We know that qualitative data focuses on categorization while quantiative data focuses on numerical analysis. We can determine if this is qualitative or quantitative since qualitative data usually uses data while quantitative involves counting or measuring numerical values.
